<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf0026cbb-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7301"><num value="7301">§ 7301.</num><heading> Suspension and repeal of permanent price support authority</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idf0026cbc-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7301/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> Agricultural Adjustment Act of 1938</heading><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="idf0026cbd-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7301/a/1"><num value="1" class="bold">(1)</num><heading class="bold"> Suspensions</heading><chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The following provisions of the Agricultural Adjustment Act of 1938 [<ref href="/us/usc/t7/s1281">7 U.S.C. 1281</ref> et seq.] shall not be applicable to the 1996 through 2001 crops of loan commodities, peanuts, and sugar and shall not be applicable to milk during the period beginning on <date date="1996-04-04">April 4, 1996</date>, and ending on <date date="2002-12-31">December 31, 2002</date>:</chapeau><subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="idf0026cbe-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7301/a/1/A"><num value="A">(A)</num><content> Parts II through V of subtitle B of title III (<ref href="/us/usc/t7/s1326–135">7 U.S.C. 1326–135</ref>1) [<ref href="/us/usc/t7/s1321">7 U.S.C. 1321</ref> et seq., 1331 et seq., 1341 et seq., 1351].</content>
</subparagraph>
<subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="idf0026cbf-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7301/a/1/B"><num value="B">(B)</num><content> Subsections (a) through (j) of section 358 (<ref href="/us/usc/t7/s1358">7 U.S.C. 1358</ref>).<ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn002336">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn002336"><num>1</num> See References in Text note below.</note></content>
</subparagraph>
